<title>USA: Riverside Group Inc Q1 shr loss widens.</title>
<headline>Riverside Group Inc Q1 shr loss widens.</headline>
<dateline>JACKSONVILLE, Fla. 1997-05-14</dateline>
<text>
<p>1997			 1996</p>
<p> Shr loss		   $0.78     loss	 $0.53</p>
<p> Net loss		   4,139     loss	 2,794</p>
<p> Revs		     160,484		    5,877</p>
<p> Avg Shrs		   5,308		    5,311</p>
<p>	 (All Data Above 000s Except Per Share Numbers)</p>
<p>NOTE: The first quarter of 1997 includes the results of the company's 52 percent owned subsidiary, Wickes Lumber Co, on a consolidated basis. During the first quarter of 1996, the company owned less than majority interst in Wickes and accounted for its investment in Wickes on the equity method.</p>
<p>The company attributed its greater loss in part to the increased ownership of Wickes.</p>
